snippet.title: Raji: An Ancient Epic | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
You're chosen by the gods. Fight demons, climb ruins and face destiny to save the human race in this lush action-adventure inspired by Indian culture.

Play Raji: An Ancient Epic on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81569945

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with 231 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
